Moody is a music track that is unlocked in the Wilderness or at the entrance to Arandar after Regicide. It also plays in Wilderness Agility Course Dungeon.

Prior to an update on 28 April 2021, the track could be unlocked west of the Chaos Temple and the hint referred to "at level 9 Wilderness". If using Classic music mode, it also plays in deep Wilderness at Deserted Keep and Scorpion Pit, where Expanse and Nightfall could originally be heard.

Location before 2021

Changes[edit | edit source]

Date Changes
25 July 2019
(update)

Moody was replaced with Attack 1 and Sad Meadow in the Battlefield and west of West Ardougne, respectively.

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • According to data crowdsourced via RuneLite before 28 April 2021, approximately 92% of players unlock the track in the Wilderness, while 8% unlock it at Arandar.
